message:
Congratulations  Roger DeHart of No More Miles Walk who walked from The Broward County Courthouse in Fort Lauderdale, FL to The Capitol in Washington D.C to raise awareness for human trafficking.
#leo #helpERASE (picture credit Ileana Almeida)
